001package org.biopax.ols.impl;

006
007import org.biopax.ols.TermPath;
008
009import java.io.Serializable;
010
011/**
012 * @author R. Cote
013 * @version $Id: TermPathBean.java,v 1.1 2006/03/23 12:32:41 rglcote Exp $
014 */
015public class TermPathBean extends AbstractTermLinker implements TermPath, Serializable {
016
017    private static final long serialVersionUID = 1L;
018
019    private long relationshipTypeId;
020
021    /**
022     * <p>Represents ...</p>
023     */
024    private long termPathId;
025
026    /**
027     * <p>Represents ...</p>
028     */
029    private int distance;
030
031    /**
032     * @return
033     */
034    public long getTermPathId() {
035        return termPathId;
036    }
037
038    /**
039     * @param _termPathId
040     */
041    public void setTermPathId(final long _termPathId) {
042        termPathId = _termPathId;
043    }
044
045    /**
046     * @return
047     */
048    public int getDistance() {
049        return distance;
050    }
051
052    /**
053     * @param _distance
054     */
055    public void setDistance(final int _distance) {
056        distance = _distance;
057    }
058
059    public long getRelationshipTypeId() {
060        return relationshipTypeId;
061    }
062
063    public void setRelationshipTypeId(long relationshipTypeId) {
064        this.relationshipTypeId = relationshipTypeId;
065    }
066}
